{"type": "article", "id": 14851, "title": "bartoli design 皮椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-14T07:09:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000306QEGzFHfV9t6ONjn7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把椅子是由 bartoli design 为意大利家具品牌 kristalia 设计的，采用了椅子最原始简单的结构，金属支架搭配木腿。座位和靠背部分包裹上全天然的皮革，在交接处进行缝线，使这把座椅有了柔和的温度，也保持了一种古朴原始的美感。这都是来自意大利定制鞋履制造商 presot 和他们从 1933 年开始的加工工艺。座面底部和背面使用船用的张紧器固定，不易开裂，在柔和中又有了粗狂感。皮革的颜色会随着时间的流逝发生改变，加深了人与椅子的互动。<a href=\"http://www.kristalia.it/design-chairs/1085-2/natural-hide-chair/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142244GVF3WDwilHs7pQLP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"340\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.41564792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142244AD7P5ExmRLfUFheO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"884\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142245d6TvEpkqIFGjg9Lx.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"526\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64303178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}